  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Care &amp; Repair: Free DIY jobs for Older People</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As we grow older basic household tasks can become very difficult to manage. People who have been house-proud all of their lives find themselves unable to maintain their homes. Ultimately this can make the difference between staying at home and moving to residential care.   Care &amp; Repair uses a pool of volunteers to carry out DIY jobs for older people free of charge. The most common services required by older people are: gardening, painting, security locks, smoke alarms, moving furniture</narrative>
  </description>
